snippet.title: Longplay of Duel Masters: Nettou! Battle Arena
snippet.description:
Longplay of Duel Masters: Nettou! Battle Arena, played as the NTSC-J version on the GameCube. This game's version was released on Dec. 18th, 2003. Tell us what you think by leaving a comment down below!
